gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 112, Nuggets 95
gameRecap.excerpt: Giannis Antetokounmpo led the Bucks with 36 points, 18 rebounds, five assists, three steals, and two blocks as the Bucks defeated the Nuggets, 112-95. Damian Lillard added 18 points and five assists in the win. Nikola Jokic led Denver with 29 points, 12 rebounds, and eight assists. The Bucks move to 35-19 as the Nuggets move to 36-18.
